  _id: act3.theo.capital.hollowfen
  _lines:
  - speaker: Wren
    text: And the village? What happens to it?
    isCloseup: 0
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 6d0c81fbb6aa448af84df638d996b866, type: 3}
  - speaker: Theo
    text: 'It goes on. Or it does not.


      That was true before I ever drove
      a wagon in here. I am only saying you would not be here to watch which.'
    isCloseup: 1
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 9d84a7b106ba24d18b3ecf1b8711076c, type: 3}
